{"tid":686470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西洋菜南街大媽大叔轉移陣地到澳門 網民大罵「只顧自己享樂，完全沒理會其他人感受」","createTime":"2018-06-01T09:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T12:43:32.000Z","uid":2547,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c1bfd5f92396a796ceec8c5830dc30519bd62b5e","tid":686470,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r2TdEOjHhnU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr2TdEOjHhnU&d=Qe4kh0FQtnTlaK23Hw01owCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=eee78211\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r2TdEOjHhnU</a><br />\n<br />\n旺角行人專用區被「殺街」，那每星期在西洋菜南街跳舞的大媽大叔們就要轉移陣地了？近日網上流傳一條片段，可以見到有大媽大叔轉戰澳門過海船，在船上走廊位「跳茶舞」，一班「觀衆」更開心地打拍子歡呼，令其他船客側目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n有網民在 Facebook 專頁「PLAY HARD 玩硬」出片，表示「尋晚發生、但其實晚晚係咁」。從片中可以見到，澳門過海船上的角落有一位女士、一位男士在走廊位「跳茶舞」，手舞足蹈了半分鐘。而周圍操普通話似是同鄉的團友就開心地打拍子、大聲歡呼，直至被一名女子上前阻止，眾人才停下來。樓主就好笑地留言說「旺角就快冇得玩，去澳門再嚟過，依家喺船到演習先！」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民客觀指出，如果他們是包船就沒有問題，但看其他乘客的反應，似乎就不是了，這嚴重影響了其他船客。所以不少網民忍不住留言，大罵「自私」、「有病」、「只顧自己享樂，完全沒理會其他人感受」、「度度都當正自己屋企咁」、「以為為大家帶嚟娛樂，實質係影響到人」又曲線笑說「唔洗比錢有得你睇想點」、「過左去（澳門）唔好返嚟啦，好好發展歌影視吧」！"},{"pid":"6b48d8da8d1a27c249511439d0192f3123c071a0","tid":686470,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:45:17.000Z","msg":"香港特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死同道好過死貧道"},{"pid":"6ccf718412f047581de8f122621e4785c0b65831","tid":686470,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"澳門唔比街頭賣藝，拉得"},{"pid":"4b648abe25355e4123f7e2918342cbe9869d46a1","tid":686470,"uid":34410,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"澳門狗千祈唔好反對呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你地咁愛國要包容下"},{"pid":"cc1e278e80d7ec8e12c62de512f7108c0053cf59","tid":686470,"uid":13257,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"正呀，過澳門，去咗唔駛番嚟喇"},{"pid":"c416713eb01dc6d5b537b14ba3c34ff03641bf4f","tid":686470,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"大家千奇唔好玩bb彈汽槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d757461284fc7928ba930df2085d88f0f844d70f","tid":686470,"uid":7169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"On9標題 點證明係同一班人"},{"pid":"f7c730cdbded1c5b5eb502526c9c63c1c3876e9a","tid":686470,"uid":19676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"澳門人唔識包容"},{"pid":"6eb99cc7d6e381df50a4a83b8ba68b9504afebb7","tid":686470,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"澳門同胞歡迎大媽跳老舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dfc7ec022ca08f775cdc8d7c63158a8193d260","tid":686470,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"你故澳門本身冇大媽舞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【警方追緝】澳門「大媽殺手」氣槍傷兩婦 疑不滿廣場舞吵鬧<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2018/04/03/010086208.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F010086208.shtml&d=Qe4kh0FQtnTlaK23Hw01owCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=eed4c870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2018/04/03/010086208.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"2dbdf8dfcc608ceed88cb691933504bb3f486dc7","tid":686470,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"2018年澳門排華"},{"pid":"ffaeb7cc508bc4663274c1d9974c69bb9ab6f8bb","tid":686470,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0